  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of unsalted butter in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the red onion and saut\u00063e until translucent, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and saut\u00063e for another minute.",
    "Add the crushed red pepper and saut\u00063e for 1 minute.",
    "Add the sliced persian cucumber and saut\u00063e until slightly tender, about 5 minutes.",
    "Sprinkle the cornstarch over the cucumber and stir to coat.",
    "Add the lemon juice and stir to combine.",
    "Stir in the salt-free seasoning blend.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a serving platter and garnish with chopped cilantro.",
